<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/jhr.94.94773.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Electronoyesella antiqua gen. et sp. nov., holotype female A wings B forewing venation C hind wing venation (ls 1, 2 - lines of setae, spv - spur vein, pst - parastigma). Scale bars: 0.2 mm (A); 0.1 mm (B, C)." ;
